The AULA 108 Pro feels amazing to type on and use overall.

You can even customize what info shows up on the screen ‚Äî super handy.
The keyboard also has a really solid build. It‚Äôs heavy in a good way and feels premium.

This is my new keyboard ‚Äî and honestly, it‚Äôs amazing.
